      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-5 max-w-3xl font-display text-4xl font-bold leading-tight grad-text md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        How to Optimise for ChatGPT
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink-200">
        ChatGPT is now one of the most-used information tools on the internet. When users ask it questions in your category, the brands it cites shape buying decisions, professional recommendations, and brand perception. This guide explains exactly how ChatGPT sources answers, how ChatGPT Search works, and the practical steps to get your brand cited accurately and consistently.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-400">
        <strong class="text-ink-300">Note:</strong> ChatGPT's behaviour changes with each model and feature update. The information below reflects publicly documented behaviour as of mid-2026. Always verify current behaviour through direct testing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Two-column: TOC sidebar + main content -->
  <div class="container-wide py-12 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[220px_1fr] lg:gap-12">

    <!-- Sticky TOC sidebar -->
